e. In the IS-ENES3 project, the web portal will be redesigned, building on experience gained during the previous projects. The next version of the portal will be built using the React framework, which allows for creating large web applications which can change data, without reloading the page. The main purpose of React is to be fast, scalable, and simple. This phase provides opportunities for users to provide another round of feedback. The climate analytics capabilities, the provided open source tools and the redesign plans are detailed in this presentation." />
